                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170416-36-off196 t18170416-36-cd197"></join> (Ann, the wife of the said James Ilbery, and others of his family being therein), and stealing twenty-five quires of writing-paper, value 20s., the property of the said 
