                     <interp inst="t18170416-36-person339" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was with Bury - He has spoken correctly. (Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>CHAPMAN'S Defence. I picked it up.</p>
